sentences: Frost is also known for playing guitar on Savatage's tour in support of Poets and Madmen in 2001 and 2002 before being dismissed from the band for unspecified reasons.
He is currently touring in  Anthrax vocalist Joey Belladonna's backing band.
Frost also currently hosts the annual ronny dude class at Brookdale College.
